documentation:
Utility to generate a tocfile.json and return its path.

It can optionally generate a corrupted toc-file with wrong first checksum.

Its basic form is:

```json
{
    "files": {
        "base-filename.00": "crc32-digest",
        ...
        "base-filename.NN": "crc32-digest",
    },
    "meta": {
        "chunk_size": 1024,
    }
}
```
